    <section>
      <h2>
        <i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation icon-yellow"></i> 4. Common
        Mistakes to Avoid
      </h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Case Sensitivity:</strong>
          Keywords (<code>SELECT</code>, <code>FROM</code>) are safe, but
          table/column names might be case sensitive. Example:
          <code>Books</code> ‚â† <code>books</code>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Missing Semicolons:</strong> Always end queries with
          <code>;</code>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Invalid Joins:</strong> Ensure join columns exist.</li>
        <li><strong>Empty Queries:</strong> Executing nothing will fail.</li>
        <li>
          <strong>AI SQL Edits:</strong> Double-check generated SQL for
          accuracy.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

